{"id": "1310443725582893139", "channel_id": "1256465710406963262", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "每位玩家每个成员为游戏的贡献都很感谢，但这不代表就拥有无视官方社区规则的特权，攻略也好、同人也好，皆如此。这一点还希望理解。", "timestamp": "2024-11-25T03:15:31.046000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1256465710406963262", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "更一波宝宝们的傻大头", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537"]}
